There should be tens of millions of yuan as bank slips per year.

45
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:36,700
But didn't he leave me a penny?

46
00:03:38,350 --> 00:03:39,610
I have no idea about it.

47
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:42,520
Tens of millions yuan?

48
00:03:42,850 --> 00:03:43,600
Nonsense.

49
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:52,829
Dad,

50
