56
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:07,990
We don't have his contact information either.

57
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,190
Mom,

58
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:16,079
we've been living together for a long time.

59
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,279
You know that

60
