63
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:24,790
I told you.

64
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,800
You have nothing to do with Liu Ming.

65
00:04:28,250 --> 00:04:28,920
From now on,

66
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:31,420
you don't have to come again.

67
00:04:31,650 --> 00:04:33,790
