83
00:05:27,990 --> 00:05:30,580
You've been working here for some days.

84
00:05:31,650 --> 00:05:34,240
Have you seen or heard anything useful?

85
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,350
Actually, I don't know much,

86
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:38,590
but I saw that shameless woman.

87
00:05:38,590 --> 00:05:40,590
She came back with Liu Ming a few times.

88
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:41,930
When they talked,

89
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:44,190
the old witch kept me away from listening.

90
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:45,200
I reminded you

91
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:47,490
