92
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:52,560
That's why you told me to keep an eye on the door,

93
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,760
right?

94
00:05:53,780 --> 00:05:54,670
Yes.

95
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:56,920
I didn't realize it.

96
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:58,970
I am so stupid.

97
00:06:00,910 --> 00:06:02,570
The old witch treats me badly.

98
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,980
You always speak for me.

99
00:06:05,650 --> 00:06:07,050
Sister, your affairs...

100
00:06:07,910 --> 00:06:08,510
I...

101
00:06:09,550 --> 00:06:10,350
Lanlan,

102
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:12,330
I need

103
00:06:12,710 --> 00:06:14,070
your help.

104
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:14,710
Say it.

105
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:17,260
The house you live in

106
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:18,430
is actually mine.

107
00:06:19,090 --> 00:06:21,230
The house ownership certificate and the purchase procedures

108
00:06:21,230 --> 00:06:23,590
were in the house I live in.

109
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,990
But later, I found

110
00:06:26,050 --> 00:06:28,790
the certificates and procedures of the two houses

111
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:29,870
were all gone.

112
00:06:30,010 --> 00:06:31,940
I guess Liu Ming took them away,

113
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:34,350
but I don’t think he took them abroad,

114
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:36,800
because such a behavior is useless to him.

115
00:06:37,290 --> 00:06:38,170
So,

116
00:06:38,659 --> 00:06:41,020
I think those should be in the house you live in.

117
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:43,360
When you do the cleaning,

118
00:06:43,710 --> 00:06:45,830
could you try to search for them?

119
00:06:45,909 --> 00:06:47,320
If you can find them,

120
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:50,640
can you take them out for me?

121
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:54,210
Now that you mention it, I seem to remember

122
00:06:54,670 --> 00:06:56,590
Liu Ming came back a few days ago

123
00:06:56,670 --> 00:06:59,080
with a small bag.

124
00:07:00,030 --> 00:07:01,560
I'll go back and look for it.

125
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,330
Thank you, Lanlan.

126
00:07:05,410 --> 00:07:06,290
But...

127
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:07,390
Tell me.

128
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:09,050
Do you have any difficulties?

129
00:07:10,790 --> 00:07:12,670
If I do so,

130
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,840
I may lose my current job.

131
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,320
But it's okay.

132
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,140
I'll play it by ear.

133
00:07:19,470 --> 00:07:20,150
No.

134
00:07:20,610 --> 00:07:22,410
If you take it out,

135
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:23,810
don't work for them.

136
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:24,660
Work for me

137
00:07:24,790 --> 00:07:26,130
if you don't mind.

138
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:26,990
OK.

139
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:30,180
-I'll pay you the same as before. -Sister, forget about the salary.

140
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:32,140
Let me do it for you first.

141
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,350
I'll go back first.

142
00:07:33,350 --> 00:07:34,700
Wait for my message.

143
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:36,080
Thank you, Lanlan.

144
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,670
Hello, mom.

145
00:07:58,490 --> 00:07:59,530
I'm working.

146
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,660
What's the matter?

147
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:04,160
I know. Stop rushing me.

148
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,860
I haven't been paid this month.

149
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,080
I'll transfer it to you

150
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,680
right away as long as I get it.

151
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,600
Stop rushing me.

152
00:08:12,230 --> 00:08:13,290
I have to go to work.

153
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,040
Don't call me.

154
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:26,990
Xiu,

155
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,880
do you have a case?

156
00:08:29,910 --> 00:08:31,910
Yes, I've been quite busy recently.

157
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:35,419
As for Wang Dafu's case,

158
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,490
I want to try it myself.

159
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:39,340
But Mr. Han asked me

160
00:08:39,169 --> 00:08:41,630
[Xiu Beibei, Intern Lawyer of the Criminal Defense Department]

161
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:42,169
to find another person to do with me.

162
00:08:42,190 --> 00:08:44,280
Qiu Hua, Mr. Han's package is here.

163
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:46,060
Just give it to me.

164
00:08:46,190 --> 00:08:47,120
Okay, thank you.

165
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,610
You're welcome.

166
00:08:47,610 --> 00:08:48,250
Thank you.

167
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,280
Mr. Han.

168
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:06,840
Mr. Han.

169
00:09:07,310 --> 00:09:09,200
I've finished all the files you gave me.

170
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,660
Now I'm here to report you.

171
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:12,950
What did you do this morning?

172
00:09:12,950 --> 00:09:15,790
