173
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:17,610
These cases are pretty interesting,

174
00:09:17,610 --> 00:09:19,840
so I borrowed some information.

175
00:09:20,530 --> 00:09:23,130
Of course, something happened to my family,

176
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:24,190
so I was delayed.

177
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,230
Sorry, sir.

178
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:26,800
I'll never do it again.

179
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:30,650
Give it to me.

180
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:33,430
I made some notes.

181
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:35,040
According to my understanding,

182
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:37,810
and combining your handling thinking,

183
00:09:38,190 --> 00:09:40,020
I summarized the way of defense.

184
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:41,840
Mr. Han, please correct me.

185
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:46,200
Have you finished these cases?

186
00:09:46,230 --> 00:09:46,910
Yes.

187
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,480
I learned a lot

188
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:49,910
from you.

189
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:51,710
The most important point is that

190
00:09:51,710 --> 00:09:53,480
law is not only the clauses,

191
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,310
but also practical experience.

192
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,050
Good.

193
00:10:08,620 --> 00:10:09,220
Not bad.

194
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:11,790
Other young lawyers

195
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:13,950
