196
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:15,410
You got it in a few days.

197
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:19,900
Work hard with me.

198
00:10:20,310 --> 00:10:21,570
I'll teach you by hand.

199
00:10:21,930 --> 00:10:22,920
Sir,

200
00:10:23,190 --> 00:10:23,960
can I

201
00:10:23,990 --> 00:10:26,800
handle the specific case with you?

202
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:29,320
You're a newcomer,

203
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:30,610
and you want to solve the case by yourself. Huh?

204
00:10:30,610 --> 00:10:31,210
Well,

205
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,710
I want to learn more from you.

206
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:35,870
And I...

207
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,390
I can't support myself

208
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:39,260
by the current basic salary.

209
00:10:39,650 --> 00:10:40,390
Sir.

210
00:10:41,330 --> 00:10:41,950
Mr. Han,

211
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:44,330
why don't you give me a case

212
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:45,450
and let me have a try?

213
00:10:45,450 --> 00:10:46,410
You guide me.

214
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:48,220
If we can earn the agent fee,

215
00:10:48,220 --> 00:10:49,480
