[Wang Dafu‘s intentional homicide]

221
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:18,000
Wang Dafu's intentional homicide.

222
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:19,870
Thank you, sir.

223
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,080
Thank you, sir.

224
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:21,950
Thank you so much.

225
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:24,190
I'll go check it out.

226
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:24,980
Thank you.

227
00:11:25,070 --> 00:11:25,590
OK.

228
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:26,270
I'll

229
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:27,470
close the door for you.

230
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:28,110
Okay.

231
00:11:28,140 --> 00:11:29,070
Please go ahead.

232
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,630
Ms. Qiu,

233
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,470
can you help me check

234
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,830
the time of the court session of this case?

235
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:48,020
Did he give you the case?

236
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:48,970
Yes.

237
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,470
Can you help me find all the information

238
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,270
of this case?

239
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:56,470
Who will be with you

240
00:11:56,470 --> 00:11:57,990
on the preparation work?

241
00:11:58,020 --> 00:11:59,150
Did Mr. Han tell you?

242
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,110
No.

243
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:02,100
He said he would give this case to me.

244
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:03,630
Did he ask you to do it alone?

245
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,350
By the way,

246
00:12:05,550 --> 00:12:07,550
how much did Mr. Han

247
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:09,640
charge the agency fee for such a case?

248
00:12:10,950 --> 00:12:14,080
This is a legal aid case assigned by the Legal Aid Center.

249
00:12:14,190 --> 00:12:15,110
There's no subsidy fee,

250
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:18,110
but some subsidies are no more than one thousand yuan.

251
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,280
It's not even enough for gas fee.

252
00:12:20,610 --> 00:12:21,410
So,

253
00:12:22,530 --> 00:12:23,440
he gives only these cases

254
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,220
to young lawyers.

255
00:12:26,110 --> 00:12:27,560
But some young lawyers

256
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:30,270
