257
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:31,150
Never mind.

258
00:12:31,210 --> 00:12:33,470
It's okay for me as long as there's a case.

259
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:37,710
May 14 is the time of the court session.

260
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:39,030
There are ten days left.

261
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,430
