262
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,620
Ms. Qiu, may I borrow a pen?

263
00:12:43,210 --> 00:12:45,620
May 14, ten days left.

264
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,080
Luo Yingzi.

265
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:48,910
If you need,

266
00:12:49,170 --> 00:12:51,890
I can help you with this case.

267
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:54,090
I won't bother you.

268
00:12:54,310 --> 00:12:55,070
Go ahead.

269
00:12:55,190 --> 00:12:56,320
Mr. Han asked me

270
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:57,950
