274
00:13:03,590 --> 00:13:04,900
I'll ask Mr. Han for it

275
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:05,940
and send the document to you.

276
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:07,660
Okay, thank you, Ms. Qiu.

277
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:08,320
It's okay.

278
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:09,080
I’m leaving.

279
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:30,470
Mr. Han.

280
00:13:31,300 --> 00:13:31,920
Yes?

281
00:13:32,430 --> 00:13:34,260
Did you hand Wang Dafu's case

282
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:36,010
to the new one, Luo Yingzi?

283
00:13:36,540 --> 00:13:38,470
She came to ask me for information.

284
00:13:41,830 --> 00:13:44,430
She is eager to express herself in the law firm.

285
00:13:46,110 --> 00:13:47,010
She is a newcomer

286
00:13:47,010 --> 00:13:49,540
and not familiar with many business matters.

287
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:51,260
Why don't I do it with her?

288
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,330
It's a waste of time.

289
00:13:52,330 --> 00:13:53,630
